<div style="width: 600px; max-height: 550px; overflow-x: auto;"><h1 class="green b_mar_ten">AVATAR PRESS: BRINGING YOU THE BLOODY BEST IN 2013</h1>
	<p class="size11"><strong>Room: 3AB</strong><em><br/>Start: 3:00PM<br/>End: 3:55PM</em></p><br/>
	<p class="rte">VP of Publishing, <b>Jim Kuhoric</b>, will lead a panel discussing Avatar's big events slated for 2013, including why this year's C-Day will be bigger than ever. With Garth Ennis returning to Crossed: Badlands in March, we will dive into details on the upcoming Crossed live-action webisodes. What writers are slated to take a stab at the Crossed universe this year? Kieron Gillen's new ongoing WWII revisionist series, Uber, launches in April - what is it all about? What does Christos Gage's Absolution sequel have in store for this summer? What is the next big project for Alan Moore, Garth Ennis, Si Spurrier? Join the panel and see what info will be revealed. It will be a bloody good time. <br></p></div>